{"ts": "2026-06-07T20:30:54.677188+00:00", "update": {"tools": {"messages": [{"type": "tool", "data": {"content": [{"type": "text", "text": "successfully downloaded text file (SHA: 04c0f5484ad13de523e75568ae9be6c1f7f2152d)", "id": "lc_11dc7556-0bd2-4d0b-80dc-594f5245e16b"}, {"type": "text", "text": "CREATE TABLE users (\n    id           BIGSERIAL PRIMARY KEY,\n    email        TEXT UNIQUE NOT NULL,\n    display_name TEXT,\n    created_at   TIMESTAMPTZ NOT NULL DEFAULT now()\n);\n", "id": "lc_f55e10d5-4cf0-40c7-834d-fab52bde3932"}], "additional_kwargs": {}, "response_metadata": {}, "type": "tool", "name": "get_file_contents", "id": "bc019117-a8ae-4558-8db1-c4bae2dbe217", "tool_call_id": "call_a97473c92f964b20a3b4358e", "artifact": null, "status": "success"}}]}}}
{"ts": "2026-06-07T20:30:54.812300+00:00", "update": {"tools": {"messages": [{"type": "tool", "data": {"content": [{"type": "text", "text": "successfully downloaded text file (SHA: 9a7ab4a43b359ce089e5b88c4f6f7515daa7431c)", "id": "lc_36ecef86-1f83-4a66-85f5-db911050e918"}, {"type": "text", "text": "CREATE TABLE sessions (\n    id          UUID PRIMARY KEY,\n    user_id     BIGINT NOT NULL REFERENCES users(id) ON DELETE CASCADE,\n    issued_at   TIMESTAMPTZ NOT NULL DEFAULT now(),\n    expires_at  TIMESTAMPTZ NOT NULL\n);\n", "id": "lc_3186ec94-dd7f-4272-9a65-5a0ae983df9c"}], "additional_kwargs": {}, "response_metadata": {}, "type": "tool", "name": "get_file_contents", "id": "80e8c84c-254e-462e-b552-2969a715c985", "tool_call_id": "call_996db430c771436cba2219c5", "artifact": null, "status": "success"}}]}}}
{"ts": "2026-06-07T20:30:54.813609+00:00", "update": {"tools": {"messages": [{"type": "tool", "data": {"content": [{"type": "text", "text": "successfully downloaded text file (SHA: 6c708c510171c17fee8c35ed6c39e513620500b8)", "id": "lc_dfee77e6-c541-4493-b2f0-a5a013d57438"}, {"type": "text", "text": "CREATE INDEX idx_sessions_user_id ON sessions(user_id);\n", "id": "lc_6e3843f7-28bf-4446-9662-f5a37986fffd"}], "additional_kwargs": {}, "response_metadata": {}, "type": "tool", "name": "get_file_contents", "id": "ceef3130-424c-4e91-aae3-1668cfebf3b7", "tool_call_id": "call_bd0baa2bb89c4e94a1b00f60", "artifact": null, "status": "success"}}]}}}
{"ts": "2026-06-07T20:31:05.382928+00:00", "update": {"model": {"messages": [{"type": "ai", "data": {"content": "Here's a walkthrough of the three database migrations in this repository, in the order they'd be applied:\n\n---\n\n### Migration 1 — `001_create_users.sql`\nCreates the **`users`** table — the foundational table for the application:\n\n| Column | Type | Notes |\n|---|---|---|\n| `id` | `BIGSERIAL` | Auto-incrementing primary key |\n| `email` | `TEXT` | Must be unique and not null |\n| `display_name` | `TEXT` | Nullable — users don't have to provide one |\n| `created_at` | `TIMESTAMPTZ` | Defaults to the current time (`now()`) |\n\n---\n\n### Migration 2 — `002_create_sessions.sql`\nCreates the **`sessions`** table — used for tracking user login sessions:\n\n| Column | Type | Notes |\n|---|---|---|\n| `id` | `UUID` | Primary key (random UUID, no auto-increment) |\n| `user_id` | `BIGINT` | Foreign key → `users(id)` with `ON DELETE CASCADE` (deleting a user wipes their sessions) |\n| `issued_at` | `TIMESTAMPTZ` | Defaults to `now()` |\n| `expires_at` | `TIMESTAMPTZ` | Must be set explicitly — no default |\n\nThis migration depends on migration 1 because it references the `users` table via a foreign key.\n\n---\n\n### Migration 3 — `003_add_session_index.sql`\nAdds an **index on `sessions.user_id`**:\n\n```sql\nCREATE INDEX idx_sessions_user_id ON sessions(user_id);\n```\n\nThis speeds up queries that look up sessions by user — for example, \"list all active sessions for a user\" or \"delete all sessions for a user.\" Without this index, PostgreSQL would have to do a full table scan on `sessions` for any `WHERE user_id = ...` query.\n\n---\n\n### Summary\n\nThe migration sequence builds a simple auth-oriented schema:\n1. **Users** are created first (the base entity).\n2. **Sessions** are created second (depends on users via FK).\n3. An **index** is added on the session's `user_id` column for query performance.\n\nThis is a clean, incremental approach — each migration adds one logical change without modifying previous migrations.", "additional_kwargs": {"refusal": null}, "response_metadata": {"token_usage": {"completion_tokens": 506, "prompt_tokens": 4382, "total_tokens": 4888, "completion_tokens_details": {"accepted_prediction_tokens": null, "audio_tokens": 0, "reasoning_tokens": 14, "rejected_prediction_tokens": null, "image_tokens": 0}, "prompt_tokens_details": {"audio_tokens": 0, "cached_tokens": 3904, "cache_write_tokens": 0, "video_tokens": 0}, "cost": 0, "is_byok": true, "cost_details": {"upstream_inference_cost": 0.0006622044, "upstream_inference_prompt_cost": 0.0002219844, "upstream_inference_completions_cost": 0.00044022}}, "model_provider": "openai", "model_name": "xiaomi/mimo-v2.5-pro-20260422", "system_fingerprint": null, "id": "gen-1780864254-ic4QwDekPwejvZ4vaEue", "finish_reason": "stop", "logprobs": null}, "type": "ai", "name": null, "id": "lc_run--019ea3c8-035e-7fc2-9892-a321aab2f4c9-0", "tool_calls": [], "invalid_tool_calls": [], "usage_metadata": {"input_tokens": 4382, "output_tokens": 506, "total_tokens": 4888, "input_token_details": {"audio": 0, "cache_read": 3904}, "output_token_details": {"audio": 0, "reasoning": 14}}}}]}}}
